Reception in honor of lt. general Seyfi Turagay. Commander Air Material Command, Turkish Air Force & Party. Host: Lt. General & Mrs. Clarence S. Irvine. US Air Force. Capitol Room 6pm."", Brigadier General Clarence Irvine enjoyed a long distinguished military career, mainly involving engineering. He served with the XXI Bomber Command (B-29's) during WWII and continued to serve throughout the 1950s and 1960s. Tags: Brigadier General Clarence S.
